Zergling/Punch:



Zergling and Punch exchanged angry looks.

"We don't take kindly to being mocked.  And you're mocking us!" Punch 
yelled, firing off a rocket from his missile launcher at Xiane.

"Zergling shall not be treated like a fool!" he fired off five rapid 
laser blasts at the heroic Maximal's torso.
